{"tid":1907764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防有情 助義工助慘死狗狗有尊嚴走最後一程","createTime":"2020-03-02T22:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T23:08:26.000Z","uid":103981,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f390de680b1fb9234a8adee76eee109f68bbc176","tid":1907764,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T22:39:36.000Z","msg":"消防有情 助義工助慘死狗狗有尊嚴走最後一程<br />\n<br />\n【動物專訊】南生圍木屋昨(3月1日)一場大火，主人沒事，狗狗卻燒死了。消防員聽到狗吠聲，急忙開喉灌救，可惜撲熄了火後，卻只找到被燒死的狗狗，消防員對在場義工坦言救不到狗狗很難過。然而，狗狗的犧牲，只換來主人一句：「不要了（狗屍）。」最後，消防員和「動人之間」義工合力抬走狗屍交善終，讓狗狗至少有尊嚴地走最後一程。<br />\n<br />\n「動人之間」義工對本報表示，他們到場時，消防員已經將狗狗救出，但狗狗已嚴重燒焦。他們向在場人士打聽，現場本來有三隻狗狗，大火發生時，另外兩隻已經逃出火場，只有這隻不知甚麼原因未有逃走。現時兩隻狗狗的下落仍不明。<br />\n<br />\n義工又表示，當時消防員聽到狗狗吠得很大聲，但現場很多石油氣罐，屋頂又倒塌，即使消防員不停向狗狗位置射水，都救不到狗狗。<br />\n<br />\n「動人之間」facebook專頁上載圖片，講述3月1日晚上的情況。當時大火向木屋蔓延，當時元朗消防局C隊的消防員聽到狗吠聲，即開喉救，但狗吠聲愈來愈弱，最終慘被燒死，而狗狗屍體旁是一個大鐵籠。<br />\n<br />\n「撲熄呢一場火警之後，消防員哥哥同我地講，聽到狗吠聲但係救唔到毛毛小朋友佢哋都好難過。」<br />\n<br />\n據知，狗狗是有主人，但經常被當成守門口狗狗，而主人得悉狗狗燒死後，只說不要狗屍了。<br />\n<br />\n義工想將狗狗屍體帶走善終，消防員見他們不夠力便幫忙抬狗狗，將狗狗屍體由河的一邊抬到對岸馬路邊，終於由善終公司帶走狗屍。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：「動人之間」facebook<br />\n<br />\n#香港動物報 #狗 #南生圍 香港消防處 Hong Kong Fire Services Department 動人之間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c36e82914f5ae9c59a688606f091c9dec78c30a","tid":1907764,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T22:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c920c4ba7bb80c9c3925de617dfe13f3feded1c4","tid":1907764,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T22:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0488ad14bc97c216901d7adbf070e1d97f078aac","tid":1907764,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T22:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9401d75866e9ffc9f707ca66d25e0df1910c93b","tid":1907764,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T22:53:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5919a14bfbcfacf4b1681b0e9294883d2bae264","tid":1907764,"uid":89375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T23:00:46.000Z","msg":"應該燒撚死個主人"},{"pid":"3a378fb741c9c8f66a71c3157af811abb2660643","tid":1907764,"uid":189608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T23:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ce2c594f36758c19ff033a0d2ea6a0b192ded8","tid":1907764,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5919a14bfbcfacf4b1681b0e9294883d2bae264","tid":1907764,"uid":89375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T23:00:46.000Z","msg":"應該燒撚死個主人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T23:08:26.000Z","msg":"南生圍不嬲都係某財團...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}